title: Jarvis v3.2 - Onepage Parallax WordPress Theme
description:
The Jarvis Theme is a very modern one page/parallax style theme that is sure to impress all of your websites visitors. If you are on the lookout for a theme which offers a huge number of development options and that taps into the very best of WordPress, look no further, you have just found it!

The Jarvis Theme has a simply huge number of amazing features and development options. This unique theme can be tailored with minimum effort and can be used for a variety of website designs, from corporate/agencies to portfolios and blogs.

Jarvis offers an endless amount of design options from a wealth of navigation options to its unlimited colors and its advanced background options such as custom backgrounds for each parallax section including full size video.

The Jarvis Theme is 100% responsive and all of the elements from the navigation to the slider will change resolution to match that of the device of your users, offering them a seamless browsing experience.

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/jarvis-onepage-parallax-wordpress-theme/5370691

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
